high_descs: Turn right and go to the sink counter.
Take the knife from the sink counter.
Go left to the black table next to the sink counter.
Cut the bread into slices.
Go right to the sink counter.
Put the knife on the counter.
Go left to the black table next to the sink counter.
Take a piece of bread.
Turn around, walk straight, turn left, walk towards the microwave, go in front of the microwave.
Put the piece of bread in the microwave, turn on the microwave, take the piece of bread out of the microwave.
Turn around, walk straight, make a right and walk towards the sink counter.
Put the piece of bread on the sink counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved piece of bread on the sink counter.

high_descs: Turn around until you see the trash can and face the white counter to your left.
Walk to the white counter and pick up the knife from the back near the sink.
Turn left and face the black table on your right.
Slice the bread in the middle of the table behind the spatula.
Turn right and face the white counter on your left.
Place the knife down behind the apple on the counter.
Turn left and face the black table on your right.
Pick up a single slice of bread on the far right side of the loaf.
Turn around until you see the stove on your right, then cross the room to face the trash can, turn right and face the microwave on your left.
Open the microwave, place the bread onto the plate, close the door, set the time to cook it, open the door and pick up the single slice of bread, and then close the door.
Turn left, walk forward until the trash can is on your right, cross the room until you reach the stove, turn right and walk to the white counter.
Place the bread to the left of the apple onto the white counter.
anns.task_desc: Heat a single piece of bread in the microwave.

high_descs: go to the counter top next to the sink with an onion and a knife
pick up the knife with the yellow handle
take the knife to the shelf next to the counter top to the left
slice the bread that is on that shelf
go back to the counter top with the onion
put the knife on the counter next to the onion
go back to the shelf with the sliced bread
pick up the end slice of bread that you cut
take the bread slice to the microwave that is in the far right hand corner of the room
put the slice of bread in the microwave and cook it, remove the slice
take the bread slice back to the counter with the onion and knife
put the bread slice on the counter to the left of the onion
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked, sliced piece of bread on the counter

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the left and face the black end table.
Cut the bread on the black end table into slices.
Take a step to the right to face the counter.
put the knife on the counter.
Step to the left to face the bread on the black end table.
Pick up a slice of bread on the black end table.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left and walk forward to face microwave.
Head the bread slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the counter.
Place the bread slice on the counter next to the potato.
anns.task_desc: To heat a bread slice and place it on the counter beside the potato.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter left of the sink
Pick up the knife behind the apple on the counter
Move slightly left to the small black table
Use the knife to slice the bread loaf on the table
Turn right and move back to the counter left of the sink
Put the knife down on the counter
Move left to the small black table
Pick up a slice of bread from the table
Turn around and walk to the microwave in the opposite corner of the kitchen
Place the bread in the microwave and cook it
Take the bread and walk back across the room to the counter left of the sink
Put the piece of bread down on the counter just left of the apple
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked bread on the kitchen counter
